quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  51,47,"Yε’de Yetumi na esii ͻsoro no, na nokorε sε, Yεn ara na Yε’bae (ͻsoro) ntrεmu no mu"
  51,48,Ɛna Yε’de asaase no nso asε hͻ; na sεdeε Y’asi atrε mu yie paa
  51,49,Adeε biara no Ya’bͻ no mmienu mmienu (onini ne ͻbedeε) sεdeε mobεkaeε
  51,50,Enti monwane nkͻ mo Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ. Nokorε sε meyε kͻkͻbͻni pefee fri Nehͻ mamo
  51,51,"Na monhwε na moanyε awurade foforͻ biara anka Nyankopͻn ho. Nokorε sε, meyε kͻkͻbͻni pefee fri Nehͻ mamo"
  51,52,"Saa ara nso na Asomafoͻ a wͻ’baa amanfoͻ a wͻ’dii wͻn anim kan no hͻ no, wͻ’ka kyerεε wͻn sε wͻ’yε nkoyaayifoͻ anaasε wͻn abobͻ adam"
  51,53,"(Tetefoͻ no) na wͻ’tuu wͻn fo saa anaa? Daabi, wͻn ara yε nnipa a wͻ’to mmara"
  51,54,"Enti twe woho fri wͻn ho, na yεmmͻ wo soboͻ"
  51,55,"Na tufo, efrisε afutuo no ho wͻ mfasoͻ ma agyidiefoͻ no"
  51,56,"Ɛnyε hwee ho nti na Mebͻͻ Jinn ne nnipa, na mmom (Mebͻͻ wͻn) sε wͻ’nsom Me"
  51,57,"Mennhwehwε akͻnhoma biara wͻ wͻn hͻ, na mennhwehwε nso sε wͻ’ma Me biribi nni"
  51,58,"Nokorε sε, Nyankopͻn ne Ɔkyε adeε Hene; Otumfoͻ Ɔhoͻdenfoͻ paa ne no"
  51,59,"Nokorε sε, wͻn a wͻ’di bͻne no wͻ bͻne so asotwee tesε wͻn a wͻ’dii kan wͻ wͻn anim no ara pεpεεpε; enti εmma wͻn mpre ho sε Memfa (asotwee no) mmra"
  51,60,Enti due nka wͻn a wͻ’po (nokorε) no wͻ wͻn Da a yahyε wͻn ho bͻ no mu